bums|title=Country Albums chart for April 6, 2013|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=March 28, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts|April 13}}\n| ''[[Based on a True Story\u2026]]''\n| {{sortname|Blake|Shelton}}\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-04-13/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for April 13, 2013|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=April 4, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts|April 20}}\n| ''[[Pioneer (The Band Perry album)|Pioneer]]''\n| {{sort|Band Perry|[[The Band Perry]]}}\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-04-20/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for April 20, 2013|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=April 17, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts|April 27}}\n| ''[[Wheelhouse (album)|Wheelhouse]]''\n| {{sortname|Brad|Paisley}}\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-04-27/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for April 27, 2013|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=April 25, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts|May 4}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''[[Based on a True Story\u2026]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\"| {{sortname|Blake|Shelton}}\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-05-04/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for May 4, 2013|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=April 25, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts|May 11}}\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-05-11/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for May 11, 2013|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=May 2, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts|May 18}}\n| ''[[Life on a Rock]]''\n| {{sortname|Kenny|Chesney}}\n| align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2013-05-18/country-albums|title=Country Albums chart for May 18, 2013|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=May 9, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n!scope=row|{{dts|May 25}